tree_elements.text: On Feb 24, 2022, Russia began a full-scale invasion of Ukraine, the largest military attack on a European state since World War II. Journalism is the first rough draft of history, high school journalists know, and this war will mark our high school years.  We wanted to understand the historical context of this war–the relationship between Russia and Ukraine and the events that led up to this attack–so we created the following timeline.

file_structural_elements.title: 10 Key Moments Leading Up To The Ukraine-Russia Conflict
